{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/chainstack/awesome-corda/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5593e237-f542-505d-8c41-11d0a8ba812b","html":"<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.corda.net/\"><img width=\"250px\" src=\"https://github.com/chainstack/awesome-corda/raw/master/project_logo.png\">\n  </a><br>\n  <a href=\"https://www.corda.net/\">Corda</a> is an open source blockchain project, designed for business from the start.\n  <br>Corda allows you to build interoperable blockchain networks that transact in strict privacy. Corda's smart contract technology allows businesses to transact directly, with value.\n  <br></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<p>Pull requests are welcome!</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#contents\">Contents</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#programming\">Programming</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#learning-and-online-courses\">Learning and online courses</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#videos\">Videos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cordapps\">CorDapps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#networks\">Networks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#misc\">Misc</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#official\">Official</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contribute\">Contribute</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.corda.net/\">Documentation</a> - Corda documentation. The go-to place for all things.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.r3.com/reports/corda-technical-whitepaper/\">Technical whitepaper</a> - Technical description of Corda.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"programming\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#programming\" aria-label=\"programming permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Programming</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.corda.net/\">Corda API reference</a> - Corda public API reference.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.corda.net/getting-set-up.html#set-up-instructions\">Development environment</a> - Step-by-step instructions to start developing on Corda.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/bluebank/braid/tree/master/braid-corda\">Braid Corda</a> - Create Braid endpoints and streams from your Corda node.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/180Protocol/codaptor\">Codaptor</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/180Protocol/codaptor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10</span></span></a> - Create REST API for any CorDapp running on a Corda node automatically.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://manosbatsis.github.io/corbeans\">Corbeans</a> - Corda integration for Spring Boot.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/LayerXcom/cordage\">Cordage</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/LayerXcom/cordage\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">51</span></span></a> - Provide modules that make the interoperability possible between Corda and other blockchains without further trusted third party.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cordalo-ch\">Cordalo</a> - Provide Corda frameworks to speed up your development in the decentralized space.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hyperledger-labs/cordentity\">Cordentity</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hyperledger-labs/cordentity\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">32</span></span></a> - Integrate <a href=\"https://www.hyperledger.org/projects/hyperledger-indy\">Hyperledger Indy</a> capabilities into Corda.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/chainstack/awesome-corda\">DAML for Corda</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/chainstack/awesome-corda\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">55</span></span></a> - DAML smart contracts for Corda.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.corda.net/demobench/\">DemoBench</a> - A standalone desktop app to configure and launch local Corda nodes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.chainstack.com/operations/corda/tools\">Interact with nodes</a> - Interact with your Corda nodes through a standalone shell, from an app, or a web server.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chainstack.com/corda/\">Nodes and networks deployment with Chainstack</a> - Easy Corda nodes and networks deployment.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://manosbatsis.github.io/partiture/\">Partiture</a> - A compact component framework for your CorDapps. Currently, its primary goal is to simplify flow composition.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/chainhaus/pycorda\">PyCorda</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/chainhaus/pycorda\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">9</span></span></a> - Access node and vault data for analytics using pandas DataFrames.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://manosbatsis.github.io/corda-rpc-poolboy/\">RPC PoolBoy</a> - RPC connection pool with support for multiple Corda nodes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.accordproject.org/news/smart-legal-contracts-on-corda/\">Smart legal contracts with Accord</a> - A reference implementation for smart legal contracts on Corda.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/manosbatsis/corda-testacles\">Testacles</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/manosbatsis/corda-testacles\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - Tools to grow CorDapp test suites.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://manosbatsis.github.io/vaultaire/\">Vaultaire</a> - Query DSL and data access utilities for Corda developers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/corda/vscode-corda\">VS Code Corda extension</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/corda/vscode-corda\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</span></span></a> - VS Code tools for developing CorDapps on the Corda platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://corda.web3j.io/\">Web3j integration for Corda</a> - A lightweight client library for working with CorDapps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cordite.foundation/\">XTS Fountain</a> - Mint XTS tokens and send them to a token account on a Corda node.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/splunkdlt/splunk-app-for-corda\">Splunk App for Corda</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/splunkdlt/splunk-app-for-corda\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - Splunk official integration app for Corda monitoring.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tutorials\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tutorials\" aria-label=\"tutorials permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tutorials</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.corda.net/tutorials-index.html\">Official Corda tutorials</a> - Learn to build and run CorDapps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/corda/samples/\">Sample CorDapps</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/corda/samples/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">94</span></span></a> - Explore the code of sample CorDapps targeting various uses.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.chainstack.com/tutorials/no-ticket-scalping-cordapp-on-corda\">No ticket scalping CorDapp</a> - Build, run, and interact with a CorDapp from scratch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@manosbatsis/vaultaire-corda-vault-queries-made-simple-d13db4147298\">Vaultaire: Corda Vault Queries Made Simple</a> - Upgrade to a clean and easy to use query DSL generated just for you.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learning-and-online-courses\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#learning-and-online-courses\" aria-label=\"learning and online courses permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Learning and online courses</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://training.corda.net/\">Official Corda Training Platform</a> - Free training platform maintained by R3 (Corda + SDKs). Self-paced with optional support.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/corda-development/\">Introduction to Corda Development</a> - A free self-paced online course.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.r3.com/training-and-certification/\">Corda developer certification</a> - Become a certified Corda developer.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"videos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#videos\" aria-label=\"videos permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Videos</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLi1PppB3-YrVq5Qy_RM9Qidq0eh-nL11N\">Corda Bootcamp</a> - A playlist of 20 videos for Corda beginners.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cordapps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cordapps\" aria-label=\"cordapps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CorDapps</h2>\n<p>Try out CorDapps and get inspired. Also explore the <a href=\"https://marketplace.r3.com/\">CorDapp marketplace</a> or add your CorDapp to the list!</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/cordite/cordite\">Cordite</a> - A collection of CorDapps providing decentralized economics and governance services.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rafaelazeredo/creditbank\">Credit scoring</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rafaelazeredo/creditbank\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</span></span></a> - A credit scoring service between the user and retail banks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ashutoshmeher-r3/auction-cordapp\">Auction</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ashutoshmeher-r3/auction-cordapp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - A demo auction CorDapp.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/corda-codeclub/marge\">Private health insurance management</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/corda-codeclub/marge\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">11</span></span></a> - A private health insurance CorDapp.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/joeldudleyr3/olive-oyl\">Sustainable fishing rights</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/joeldudleyr3/olive-oyl\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5</span></span></a> - A CorDapp to manage fishing rights.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"networks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#networks\" aria-label=\"networks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Networks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://corda.network/\">Corda Network</a> - A global production network run by the Corda Network Foundation.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://corda.network/participation/preprod.html\">Corda Pre-Production Network</a> - A UAT network providing a pre-production environment run by the Corda Network Foundation.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.corda.net/corda-testnet-intro.html\">Corda Testnet</a> - A free public testnet with minimal permissions run by the the Corda Network Foundation.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cordite.foundation/\">Cordite Network</a> - A testnet open to anyone run by the Cordite Foundation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://slack.corda.net/\">Slack</a> - Talk to the Corda community.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://groups.io/g/corda-dev\">Mailing list</a> - Join the Corda developers mailing list.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Corda-Code-Club/\">Corda Code Club</a> - Corda Developer Meetup in London.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"misc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#misc\" aria-label=\"misc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Misc</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://lankydan.dev\">Corda developer blog</a> - A very helpful blog from a Corda developer.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"official\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#official\" aria-label=\"official permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Official</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.corda.net/\">Corda website</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contribute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contribute\" aria-label=\"contribute permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h